text: Richard Beauchamp (April 8, 1901 - June 30, 1975) was an American diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1975 deaths Category:American male divers Category:Olympic divers of the United States Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:People from Leavenworth, Kansas
